dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kevin Barnes. May I have your name, please?
Hi Kevin, my name is Jennifer Stewart.
Nice to meet you, Jennifer. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's zero seven eight four five.
Thank you, Jennifer. Can you confirm the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident?
It's a two zero one eight Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for the information. Jennifer, what is your current address for our records?
My address is six five three Pine Street, Cityville.
Thank you for updating your address, Jennifer. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Kevin.
You're welcome, Jennifer. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
